Uses of Package
de.wwu.muggl.vm.execution

Packages that use de.wwu.muggl.vm.execution
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.bytecode Provides the classes for byte code instructions. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.general Provides abstract superclasses for the instruction classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.interfaces Provides interfaces for the byte code instructions. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.interfaces.control Provides interfaces for marking the behaviour of instructions with regard to the control-flow. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced.quick Provides QuickInstruction classes which can be used to speed up execution. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced.replacer Provides ReplacingInstruction classes that can be used to set QuickInstruction classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.typed Provides classes that provide functionality for typed instructions. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.generating Provides interfaces for generator classes, a ChoicePoint implementation for generators and a subpackage with concrete generator implementations. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.searchAlgorithms Provides search algorithm related packages. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.searchAlgorithms.depthFirst Provides the depth first search algorithm implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.symbolic.searchAlgorithms.iterativeDeepening Provides the iterative deepening depth first search algorithm implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm Provides the abstract virtual machine implementation along with packages for the structures it uses. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.exceptions Provides the Exception handler used by the virtual machine alone with the VmRuntimeException class which represents runtime exceptions in this virtual machine implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.execution Provides algorithms needed during the execution and other execution related classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.impl.logic   
de.wwu.muggl.vm.impl.real Provides the real virtual machine implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.impl.symbolic Provides the symbolic virtual machine implementation. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.impl.symbolic.exceptions Provides the symbolic exception handler used by the symbolic virtual machine. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.initialization Provides initialization classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.initialization.strings Provides the string cache and auxiliary classes.
